{"tid":2452072,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有左呢個新技術，高像素機變左多舊魚 (多雞腸慎入)","createTime":"2021-03-18T14:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T05:07:29.000Z","uid":191921,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"05e5607558b5be7ee06b11f084a4cfda26b0228b","tid":2452072,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T14:36:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://blog.adobe.com/en/publish/2021/03/10/from-the-acr-team-super-resolution.html#gs.wiariw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.adobe.com%2Fen%2Fpublish%2F2021%2F03%2F10%2Ffrom-the-acr-team-super-resolution.html%23gs.wiariw&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=7ccb723d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.adobe.com/en/publish/2021/03/10/from-the-acr-team-super-resolution.html#gs.wiariw</a><br />\n<br />\n睇圖真係幾誇張"},{"pid":"a55ef61b7126f08a961a68ea5a46aaeeb198cf4d","tid":2452072,"uid":12443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"s3終於可以整大翻啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a314c1bf8750a638e7aa8a238a2c3818f0665fe","tid":2452072,"uid":28280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T00:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b755100cbe66aac0c94f51db444c644cdf4eff20","tid":2452072,"uid":191921,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a55ef61b7126f08a961a68ea5a46aaeeb198cf4d","tid":2452072,"uid":12443,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T16:06:48.000Z","msg":"s3終於可以整大翻啲相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:07:16.000Z","msg":"用2014年釋出的僅僅1600萬畫素的富士X-T1相機用廣角拍攝的手辦，放大到4200萬畫素。經過Adobe Camera Raw 13.2的AI超解析度放大400%後，眼睛貼紙的細節依然清晰明麗，也沒有過度銳化的效果。<br />\n<br />\n筆者對比了用索尼RX1R2相機拍攝的，原生的4200萬畫素的原圖，和松下S5相機拍攝的由2400萬畫素感測器利用堆疊高解析度模式合成的9600萬畫素的圖，原生4200萬畫素的原圖噪點和細節都是墊底。<br />\n<br />\n這個結果我也是比較意外。原生4200萬畫素的圖並沒有在放大後的細節上佔什麼優勢。AI超解析度的演算法的結果完全不比原生高畫素的細節差"},{"pid":"21da14e89f25bd3df04840751969c062c3b19efa","tid":2452072,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a314c1bf8750a638e7aa8a238a2c3818f0665fe","tid":2452072,"uid":28280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T00:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:08:21.000Z","msg":"實戰例子。<br />\n<br />\n上圖是用廣角拍攝的公園一景，完全談不上構圖，僅僅是拍到了一隻鳥兒<br />\n<br />\n而經過了4倍倍線超解析度放大，和剪裁重新構圖，就可以獲得鳥兒的清晰影像，連長焦都省了。以後打鳥，都不用什麼長焦了，廣角都能打鳥你信？<br />\n<br />\n而高畫素相機，在獲取清晰圖片的過程中，本身就會遇到很多問題，例如富士最近剛發售的GF100S中畫幅相機，擁有一億畫素的超高解析度，但一億畫素的畫素量，導致你拍照的時候稍微一點點顫抖都會導致糊片，即便有機身防抖鏡頭防抖加持，出片率依然是沒有低畫素機拍攝出片率來得高的，那麼AI超解析度技術的普及，還是有助於更高的出片率，普通相機拍攝，AI超解析度放大，就能獲得接近高解析度原片的清晰度，而且隨著技術的迭代，這種效果只會無限接近於原片，差距越來越小，那麼高畫素機本身的價值。。。。。。"},{"pid":"4b83af4bd402b2a2cc54ebeb97744e08c77d3066","tid":2452072,"uid":168394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"陳年流出救星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5429010111bc42d576271e161cc59d9d78505e06","tid":2452072,"uid":191921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4b83af4bd402b2a2cc54ebeb97744e08c77d3066","tid":2452072,"uid":168394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:25:37.000Z","msg":"陳年流出救星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://swiftandtit.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/camera-raw-comparison-scaled.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fswiftandtit.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2Fcamera-raw-comparison-scaled.jpg&h=a59883bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n效果幾正"},{"pid":"ad362a60da4844124d40c9161976d66cbd1938e1","tid":2452072,"uid":168394,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"係咪終於可以睇到黑鮑係咪真係咁黑<img src=\"/